#~ msgstr ""
#~ "Zastąp listy rozwijane wariantów próbnikami na stronach pojedynczego "
#~ "produktu."

#~ msgid ""
#~ "Used for any attribute you have not given an explicit type. Attributes with "
#~ "no colours configured automatically fall back to the dropdown, so this is "
